id: pm-cn0c
title: "composeExtensionPackage: author-once capstone returning { module, manifest }"
description: "Add composeExtensionPackage(blueprint, identity): ExtensionPackage to src/sdk/compose.ts — the author-once capstone that unifies composeExtension + synthesizeExtensionManifest. Synthesize the complete least-privilege manifest from the blueprint + identity, then compose the ExtensionModule with that synthesized manifest set as its authoritative in-module mirror, so the runtime module and the on-disk manifest.json are generated from one source and can never drift. Returns { module, manifest }: write module as the package entry default export, write manifest as manifest.json. Pure assembler (no validation/loading); pairs with preflightExtension for the verify step. Completes the declarative loop end-to-end: author (define*) -> assemble modularly (merge) -> ship both halves (composeExtensionPackage)."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 2
